title: Tube & Berger - Deeper Sessions (2014) (320kbps) (AciDToX8)
description:
Tube & Berger - Deeper Sessions (2014) 

                       Deep House | Armada Music Bundles  

            320 kbps | MP3 | unmixed | 2014-11-21 | 03:06:09 | 427 Mb


Based on their radio show of the same name, 'Deeper Sessions' is a mix compilation of the defining Tube & Berger sound. Featuring releases from Booka Shade, Kolsch, 16 Bit Lolitas and many more, this compilation is a collection of the 16 greatest tunes from the show, provided both separately and as a seamless, continuous mix. Energetic tunes like 'Discopolis' and 'Beat Organ' finish the record off in style, while 'Embargo' drifts into uncharted, magically deep territory. 'Walking Back' sets a solid groove, preceded by the soulful vocals of Tube & Berger's remix of 'Let Me Down'. From vocal cuts to techy grooves, melodic gems to straight beats, 'Deeper Sessions' has all bases covered.
